Swaryszewo  is a settlement in the administrative district of Gmina Nowy Dwór Gdański, within Nowy Dwór Gdański County, Pomeranian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  east of Nowy Dwór Gdański and  east of the regional capital Gdańsk.
